{
  "name": "Se7enSlasher + AdamFX + martin - Ultra-Ravy Kaleidoscope",
  "description": "",
  "init_eqs": "dirx = 1;",
  "frame_eqs": "dec_med = pow (0.7, 30/fps);\ndec_slow = pow (0.9, 30/fps);\nbeat = max (max (bass, mid), treb);\navg = avg*dec_slow + beat*(1-dec_slow);\nis_beat = above(beat, avg+peak) * above (time, t0+.1);\nt0 = is_beat*time + (1-is_beat)*t0;\npeak = is_beat * beat + (1-is_beat)*peak*dec_med;\nindex = (index + is_beat) %16;\nindex2 = (index2 + is_beat*bnot(index))%4;\n\nq20 = avg;\nq21 = beat;\nq22 = peak;\nq23 = index;\nq24 = is_beat;\nq26 = bass + mid + treb;\n//q29 = 2 * (index2%2-.5);\nq25 = min(1,q22/2);\n\nk1 =  is_beat*equal(index%4,0);\np1 =  k1*(p1+1) + (1-k1)*p1;\np2 = dec_med * p2+ (1-dec_med)*p1;\nrott = p2 * 3.1416/4;\nq1 = cos(rott);\nq2 = sin(rott);\nq3 = -q2;\nq4 = q1;\n\n\n//q27 = index;\nq28 = index2;\n\nmov = mov*dec_med + (1-dec_med)*above(index%8,2);\nmovez = movez + 1/fps*mov;\nq30 = movez;\n//**************************\n\nq8 = movex; q9 = movey;\n\ntrel1 = trel1 + (q1*q22*3)/fps;\ntrel2 = trel2 + (q2*q22*2)/fps;\ntrel3 = trel3 + 4*(1-mov)/fps;\ntrel4 = trel4 + 1 * mov/fps;\n\nq11 = .3*sin(trel1);\nq12 = .1*cos(trel2);\nq13 = 8 + 6*sin(trel3);\n\nq14 = .3*sin(trel2);\nq15 = .2*cos(trel3) ;\nq16 = 6 + 3*sin(trel1);\n\nq17 = .3*sin(trel4);\nq18 = .3*cos(trel2);\nq19 = 3 + sin(trel3);\n\ntrot = trel1/2;\ntrot = index2*6.28/4;\nq5 = cos(trot);\nq6 = sin(trot);\nq7 = -q6;\nq8 = q5;\n\n\ntexdissolve = texdissolve+(q22/25);\nq32 = texdissolve;\n\nq29 = comprandr = if(equal(q24, 1), rand(1), comprandr);\nq30 = comprandg = if(equal(q24, 1), rand(1), comprandg);\nq31 = comprandb = if(equal(q24, 1), rand(1), comprandb);",
